1
00:00:10,860 --> 00:00:12,780
♪The wind blows, but I don't see you♪

2
00:00:12,820 --> 00:00:14,740
♪I added a few more strokes♪

3
00:00:14,740 --> 00:00:17,380
♪To the ending♪

4
00:00:17,580 --> 00:00:21,580
♪With the flowers falling
and the time passing♪

5
00:00:21,860 --> 00:00:24,140
♪Leaving only memories behind♪

6
00:00:24,300 --> 00:00:28,220
♪The wind blows from a long distance♪

7
00:00:28,340 --> 00:00:31,020
♪Yet, you didn't show up♪

8
00:00:31,140 --> 00:00:33,140
♪This love is full of regrets♪

9
00:00:33,300 --> 00:00:37,420
♪You are but a dream
in this fleeting life♪

10
00:00:40,260 --> 00:00:41,260
[Part For Ever]

11
00:00:41,260 --> 00:00:42,000
[Adapted from the novel by Jing Mo,]

12
00:00:42,000 --> 00:00:42,900
[My Lord,
Madam Doesn't Want to See You Again]

13
00:00:42,900 --> 00:00:44,780
[Episode 9]

14
00:01:01,670 --> 00:01:02,600
How could it be you?

15
00:01:03,460 --> 00:01:09,100
♪A play of sorrows and joys,
your role, my outline♪

16
00:01:09,300 --> 00:01:14,460
♪Though the dream is over,
the feelings are hard to let go♪

17
00:01:15,240 --> 00:01:17,480
If that little girl hadn't asked me
to come see you

18
00:01:17,680 --> 00:01:19,090
I wouldn't have taken the risk
of coming here.

19
00:01:19,890 --> 00:01:21,200
Since you think it's dangerous here,

20
00:01:23,120 --> 00:01:24,200
why don't you leave quickly?

21
00:01:27,340 --> 00:01:32,900
♪A song asking about heart matters,
but who will answer?♪

22
00:01:33,420 --> 00:01:38,700
♪An old dream with infatuation
and resentment and complications♪

23
00:01:38,740 --> 00:01:40,140
♪You sing for me♪

24
00:01:41,650 --> 00:01:43,370
I see your body has recovered.

25
00:01:47,530 --> 00:01:48,450
Or should I say,

26
00:01:49,650 --> 00:01:51,010
You were just seizing the momentum

27
00:01:51,450 --> 00:01:52,450
and taking advantage of the situation?

28
00:01:54,370 --> 00:01:55,840
My body has always been strong.

29
00:01:56,650 --> 00:01:58,650
I'm fitter than most people.

30
00:01:59,810 --> 00:02:01,930
Your body is so extraordinarily tough

31
00:02:03,010 --> 00:02:04,120
that any poison

32
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:06,200
would have its effects reduced on you.

33
00:02:07,010 --> 00:02:08,170
That's because my cultivation

34
00:02:08,170 --> 00:02:09,520
is much higher than others'.

35
00:02:11,170 --> 00:02:12,800
You are also more thick-skinned
than others.

36
00:02:15,890 --> 00:02:17,640
You are a fragile person.

37
00:02:18,250 --> 00:02:19,130
It's better to stay away.

38
00:02:21,850 --> 00:02:23,290
I'll stay here today.

39
00:02:23,290 --> 00:02:24,130
I'm not going anywhere.

40
00:02:32,080 --> 00:02:33,170
I'm not a prisoner.

41
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:34,730
You don't have to guard me.

42
00:02:37,850 --> 00:02:39,010
Are you afraid

43
00:02:39,480 --> 00:02:41,730
that I will do a sneak attack
while you are asleep?

44
00:02:42,600 --> 00:02:43,570
How could I be afraid of you?

45
00:02:49,600 --> 00:02:51,040
I just don't want to see you.

46
00:02:52,570 --> 00:02:54,570
You won't see me when you're asleep.

47
00:02:54,890 --> 00:02:56,040
What if your soul

48
00:02:56,450 --> 00:02:57,890
appears in my dreams and spies on me.

49
00:02:58,290 --> 00:02:59,520
The divine punishment is not true.

50
00:02:59,890 --> 00:03:00,920
Do you seriously believe
in souls and spirits?

51
00:03:12,820 --> 00:03:14,180
[City Lord's Mansion]

52
00:03:14,470 --> 00:03:15,360
People of Canglong City.

53
00:03:16,280 --> 00:03:16,910
People of Canglong City,

54
00:03:17,080 --> 00:03:18,000
listen to me.

55
00:03:18,910 --> 00:03:21,310
There is an epidemic outside the city,

56
00:03:21,680 --> 00:03:23,400
but we shouldn't blame His Lordship.

57
00:03:23,710 --> 00:03:24,710
He is also a victim.

58
00:03:25,120 --> 00:03:25,430
Look,

59
00:03:25,710 --> 00:03:27,400
he has been unconscious on the bed
since yesterday

60
00:03:27,710 --> 00:03:28,840
and has yet to wake up.

61
00:03:29,310 --> 00:03:30,400
His lordship is unconscious?

62
00:03:30,840 --> 00:03:32,360
Isn't it because
he took over power by force

63
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:33,840
and caused heaven's displeasure?

64
00:03:34,120 --> 00:03:35,190
Why should we follow him

65
00:03:35,190 --> 00:03:36,080
and suffer with him?

66
00:03:36,190 --> 00:03:36,710
Exactly.

67
00:03:36,710 --> 00:03:38,470
Why should we suffer together?

68
00:03:38,470 --> 00:03:39,240
Everyone be quiet.

69
00:03:39,240 --> 00:03:39,840
Quiet.

70
00:03:39,960 --> 00:03:42,150
It is someone else
who is causing harm to Canglong City.

71
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:44,120
It's Su Wan'er.

72
00:03:45,030 --> 00:03:45,560
Su Wan'er?

73
00:03:45,560 --> 00:03:46,360
People of Canglong City,

74
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:48,590
from the Astrology Officer's observation
of the skies,

75
00:03:49,120 --> 00:03:51,470
Her Ladyship Su Wan'er
is the evil lone star.

76
00:03:51,630 --> 00:03:52,710
Her fate is extremely cursed.

77
00:03:53,150 --> 00:03:54,430
She first caused the death
of the previous City Lord.

78
00:03:54,560 --> 00:03:55,520
Now, she is causing harm
to His Lordship,

79
00:03:55,800 --> 00:03:56,870
involving the people.

80
00:03:57,400 --> 00:03:59,000
She should be driven out
of the City Lord's Mansion

81
00:03:59,400 --> 00:04:01,190
to stop her from causing further harm
to Canglong City.

82
00:04:01,190 --> 00:04:02,590
Yes, cast Su Wan'er out.

83
00:04:02,590 --> 00:04:03,400
Cast Su Wan'er out.

84
00:04:03,400 --> 00:04:07,000
Come out.

85
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:28,920
Did you stay with me all night?

86
00:04:36,390 --> 00:04:37,190
Ling.

87
00:04:37,190 --> 00:04:38,270
You have finally woken up.

88
00:04:38,390 --> 00:04:39,430
I was worried about you all night.

89
00:04:39,630 --> 00:04:40,920
Let me check
if there is any residual poison.

90
00:04:44,390 --> 00:04:45,190
Where is Su Wan'er?

91
00:04:47,920 --> 00:04:49,160
To think that you spared her life.

92
00:04:49,430 --> 00:04:50,310
Who would've thought

93
00:04:50,310 --> 00:04:52,310
she would run away overnight
while you were poisoned?

94
00:05:03,240 --> 00:05:05,680
She has flawless pale skin.

95
00:05:06,040 --> 00:05:08,720
I wonder what she feels like.

96
00:05:09,750 --> 00:05:10,560
Why do you think

97
00:05:10,560 --> 00:05:13,310
the brothel keeper would buy her
at a high price?

98
00:05:13,830 --> 00:05:15,070
No, that wench ran away.

99
00:05:22,390 --> 00:05:23,560
Don't come over here.

100
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:30,240
Kill me if you can.

101
00:05:30,430 --> 00:05:31,270
Kill you?

102
00:05:31,510 --> 00:05:33,310
Why don't I savor you instead?

103
00:05:36,600 --> 00:05:37,600
Let go of me.

104
00:05:39,750 --> 00:05:41,120
Don't touch me.

105
00:05:44,190 --> 00:05:44,870
Let me go.

106
00:06:06,220 --> 00:06:09,140
♪The lush and fragrant grass
made longing hard to endure♪

107
00:06:09,140 --> 00:06:12,620
♪Can I entrust my heart to you?♪

108
00:06:12,780 --> 00:06:15,580
♪This love is hard to fade away
as it twists and turns endlessly♪

109
00:06:15,620 --> 00:06:18,940
♪On the path of emotions♪

110
00:06:19,140 --> 00:06:22,780
♪Reflected in a mirror
by moonlight through a window♪

111
00:06:22,980 --> 00:06:25,660
♪How much is your affection?♪

112
00:06:25,940 --> 00:06:31,980
♪When the time to love is not right,
worldly matters make it hard to endure♪

113
00:06:32,060 --> 00:06:34,700
♪Amid all worldly matters,
I only devote to one person♪

114
00:06:34,780 --> 00:06:39,500
♪Love is silent, but it leaves traces
as deep as the sea ♪

115
00:06:39,620 --> 00:06:45,300
♪I accompany you
for a part of the journey♪

116
00:06:45,420 --> 00:06:47,860
♪Our longing for each other
guides us through countless lives♪

117
00:06:47,900 --> 00:06:52,980
♪The flowers of the entire city
blossom for a person♪

118
00:06:53,060 --> 00:06:58,380
♪Let's spend
the rest of our lives together♪

119
00:07:12,820 --> 00:07:16,020
♪My dream is rising
in my heart like a spiral♪

120
00:07:16,100 --> 00:07:19,300
♪The fate
of our meeting has been decided♪

121
00:07:19,380 --> 00:07:22,300
♪Your smile under the lantern♪

122
00:07:22,380 --> 00:07:25,700
♪Stirs up my thoughts like crazy♪

123
00:07:26,020 --> 00:07:29,660
♪The moonlight is dancing
and the fireflies are twinkling♪

124
00:07:29,740 --> 00:07:32,700
♪No one knows
how deep my love is for you♪

125
00:07:37,560 --> 00:07:38,390
Sorry.

126
00:07:39,240 --> 00:07:40,040
I'm late.

127
00:07:42,120 --> 00:07:43,070
I'll take you home.

128
00:08:05,270 --> 00:08:06,870
Thank you for today.

129
00:08:09,740 --> 00:08:10,710
If you want to thank me,

130
00:08:11,180 --> 00:08:11,980
there are many ways.

131
00:08:12,830 --> 00:08:13,510
How exactly

132
00:08:16,390 --> 00:08:17,480
would you like to thank me?

133
00:08:24,310 --> 00:08:25,070
Oh, right.

134
00:08:25,430 --> 00:08:27,480
You already know everything Niyue did.

135
00:08:27,750 --> 00:08:28,830
What will you do to her?

136
00:08:31,160 --> 00:08:32,080
How do you want to deal with her?

137
00:08:32,720 --> 00:08:34,910
Give her the punishment she deserves.

138
00:08:38,240 --> 00:08:39,670
Do you still want to protect her?

139
00:08:45,480 --> 00:08:46,550
In Canglong City,

140
00:08:47,480 --> 00:08:48,360
right and wrong

141
00:08:48,910 --> 00:08:50,360
are all up to me.

142
00:08:52,960 --> 00:08:54,440
How can you not tell right from wrong?

143
00:08:55,320 --> 00:08:56,120
Do you think you deserve

144
00:08:56,750 --> 00:08:58,840
to ride a horse with me?

145
00:09:05,390 --> 00:09:06,320
Ling Xiao.

146
00:09:06,960 --> 00:09:07,870
Ling Xiao.

147
00:09:13,510 --> 00:09:15,360
A severe case of cold syndrome.

148
00:09:15,360 --> 00:09:17,360
It's harder and harder
to control myself.

149
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:20,670
Fortunately, I sent her away.

150
00:09:47,390 --> 00:09:48,200
Ling Xiao.

151
00:09:51,630 --> 00:09:52,440
Ling Xiao.

152
00:10:12,300 --> 00:10:19,580
♪A thousand journeys end,
transcending eternity♪

153
00:10:19,660 --> 00:10:26,220
♪Sounds of solitary mourning♪

154
00:10:27,140 --> 00:10:34,300
♪Life passes quickly,
like how dusk arrives suddenly♪

155
00:10:35,020 --> 00:10:40,900
♪The evening snowy wind is too strong
that the boat cannot sail♪

156
00:10:40,980 --> 00:10:48,340
♪The peach blossom falls on my bed,
the moon is as bright as ever♪

157
00:10:48,500 --> 00:10:55,740
♪With a bottle of wine
by the river, I sing softly♪

158
00:10:55,860 --> 00:10:59,460
♪Not going back, not looking back♪

159
00:10:59,580 --> 00:11:03,980
♪Even good times are spent in vain♪

160
00:11:04,740 --> 00:11:09,420
♪Trapped in the mornings
and the evenings♪

161
00:11:10,420 --> 00:11:17,780
♪As the flames of life extinguish,
it's all nothingness in the end♪
